1953;;36 Hours;;British;;Montgomery Tully;;Dan Duryea, Elsie Albiin;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/36_Hours_(1953_film);;Bill Rogers (Dan Duryea), an American jet pilot, comes to England to find out why he hasn't heard from his wife lately. Upon his arrival, he learns that his wife has been murdered, and that he's the prime suspect. With only 36 hours at his disposal, Rogers takes it upon himself to track down the actual killer.